<b>Compilation</b><br/>
Program is compiled by ant using: <i>ant -f &lt;path to folder containing build.xml&gt; -Dnb.internal.action.name=rebuild clean jar</i><br/>
<br/>
<b>Running</b><br/>
program can be started by command: <i>java -jar BSCIdeas_intro.jar<i/> from build destination directory.<br/>
<ul>
    <li>optional parameters:</li>
    <ul>
        <li><b>payments file</b> as first parameter in format of absolute path or relative to run space</li>
    </ul>
    <li>supported commands</li>
    <ul>
        <li><b>add payment</b> formated as CURRENCY AMMOUNT. Ex: EUR 344<br/>Note: currently supported list of currencies: USD, HKD, RMB, NZD, GPB, EUR, CZK</li>
        <li><b>load payments from file</b> formated as $load &lt;path to file&gt; in case of loading multiple files, all will be imported. In case of corrupted file, no data will be imported.
        <li><b>quit</b> to exit application</li>
    </ul>
<ul/>

